name: ThaiDollLikeness (v1.0)
description:
Hi, this is author Kbr, this LORA was the result of the polling I did on Twitter awhile ago, it has finally been finished after many making several versions, and this version is the one I've deemed the best. May continue to update this in the future.

(Please double check the naming of the LORA file when using sample images generation data, Civitai love to rename the LORA file automatically into something different)

If you are wondering where are the older versions of my other LORAs, you can find them here on huggingface: https://huggingface.co/Kanbara/doll-likeness-series

My Twitter: https://twitter.com/KbrLoras
My Pixiv: https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/92373922

I usually post my works on Twitter and Pixiv.

Please consider supporting me financially at: https://ko-fi.com/kbrloras

It takes time and effort to collect training materials, training, testing LORAS, I would appreciate your support!

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Introduction
1. This version is the base version of ThaiDollLikeness, I might give it an update in the future for featuring additional sets of faces.

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (For realistic models)

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • Steps: 20 to 35

  • Clipskip: 1 or 2

  • Upscaler : Latent (bicubic antialiased)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: anywhere between 0.2 to 0.7 are recommended

  • Denoise strength for img2img: 0.4 to 0.7

  • It is also recommended to mix this LORA with my other DollLikeness LORAs for interesting effects
